{\b\fs32 1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY}
\par
{\fs20 Spectra Media Agent is an advanced agentic platform that automates the creation, deployment, and optimization of marketing campaigns across multiple advertising platforms including Google Ads and Facebook Ads. The system leverages artificial intelligence agents to autonomously manage complex marketing workflows while maintaining human oversight and control.}
\par
{\fs20 Key Capabilities:}
\par
{\fs20 • Autonomous strategy generation based on business inputs}
\par
{\fs20 • Automated campaign creation and deployment across multiple platforms}
\par
{\fs20 • Real-time performance monitoring and analysis}
\par
{\fs20 • AI-driven optimization and recommendations}
\par
{\fs20 • Multi-platform budget allocation and management}
\par
{\fs20 • Integration with Stripe billing for cost tracking}
\par
{\fs20 • Role-based access control and permission management}
\par
