{\b\fs32 3. AGENT DESIGN \\'26 WORKFLOW}
\par
{\fs20 3.1 PRIMARY AGENTS}
\par
{\fs20 STRATEGY GENERATION AGENT}
\par
{\fs20 Purpose: Generate and refine marketing strategies}
\par
{\fs20 Implementation: GenerateStrategy Job + StrategyGenerator Service}
\par
{\fs20 Input: Business details, performance data, seasonal adjustments}
\par
{\fs20 Output: Platform-specific strategies with bidding parameters}
\par
{\fs20 AI Integration: Uses Google Gemini 3.x API for strategy synthesis}
\par
{\fs20 PERFORMANCE ANALYSIS AGENT}
\par
{\fs20 Purpose: Collect, analyze, and report on campaign metrics}
\par
{\fs20 Implementation: FetchGoogleAdsPerformanceData, FetchFacebookAdsPerformanceData}
\par
{\fs20 Input: Campaign IDs, date ranges}
\par
{\fs20 Output: Aggregated performance metrics with insights}
\par
{\fs20 Features: Raw metric collection, currency conversion, anomaly detection}
\par
{\fs20 CAMPAIGN DEPLOYMENT AGENT}
\par
{\fs20 Purpose: Create and launch campaigns on advertising platforms}
\par
{\fs20 Implementation: DeployCampaignToGoogleAds, DeployCampaignToFacebook}
\par
{\fs20 Input: Campaign specifications, creative assets}
\par
{\fs20 Output: Campaign creation confirmations with platform IDs}
\par
{\fs20 Features: Automated asset upload, validation, platform-specific optimization}
\par
{\fs20 OPTIMIZATION AGENT}
\par
{\fs20 Purpose: Recommend and apply optimizations based on performance}
\par
{\fs20 Implementation: GenerateOptimizationRecommendations, ApplyOptimizations}
\par
{\fs20 Input: Performance metrics, historical data}
\par
{\fs20 Output: Optimization recommendations with implementation details}
\par
{\fs20 Features: A/B testing suggestions, budget reallocation, bidding adjustments}
\par
{\fs20 3.2 AGENT WORKFLOW}
\par
{\fs20 User Input}
\par
{\fs20     ↓}
\par
{\fs20 Strategy Generation → Strategy Approval}
\par
{\fs20     ↓}
\par
{\fs20 Campaign Creation → Asset Upload}
\par
{\fs20     ↓}
\par
{\fs20 Campaign Deployment → Platform Sync}
\par
{\fs20     ↓}
\par
{\fs20 Performance Monitoring ← Continuous Fetching}
\par
{\fs20     ↓}
\par
{\fs20 Analysis \\'26 Recommendations}
\par
{\fs20     ↓}
\par
{\fs20 Optimization Implementation}
\par
{\fs20     ↓}
\par
{\fs20 Feedback Loop (repeat)}
\par
{\fs20 3.3 JOB QUEUE INTEGRATION}
\par
{\fs20 All agents are implemented as Laravel Jobs dispatched through the queue system:}
\par
{\fs20 - Asynchronous execution prevents blocking user requests}
\par
{\fs20 - Retry logic with exponential backoff for reliability}
\par
{\fs20 - Circuit breaker pattern for external API calls}
\par
{\fs20 - Distributed locking to prevent concurrent conflict}
\par
{\fs20 - Comprehensive error logging and alerting}
\par
