{\fs20 - Database encryption for sensitive data fields}
\par
{\fs20 - No plaintext storage of API keys or tokens}
\par
{\fs20 credential Management:}
\par
{\fs20 - Refresh tokens encrypted before storage}
\par
{\fs20 - Automatic token rotation on use}
\par
{\fs20 - Secure deletion of revoked credentials}
\par
{\fs20 - Audit logging of credential access}
